videos.headline: Corral pulls off an impressive run on 4th down
videos.description: Matt Corral jukes out one defender, trucks another on his way to a first down.

videos.headline: Corral is carted off the field after injuring his leg in Sugar Bowl
videos.description: Matt Corral gets sacked and is carted off the field after injuring his leg vs. Baylor.

videos.headline: Baylor takes 96-yard INT return to the house
videos.description: Al Walcott intercepts the tipped pass and it takes it 96 yards for a Baylor touchdown.

videos.description: Baylor comes up with three interceptions and several key sacks in a 21-7 Sugar Bowl victory over Ole Miss.

videos.headline: No. 8 Ole Miss falls to No. 9 Baylor in Sugar Bowl
videos.description: The Rebels throw three interceptions and struggle offensively following Matt Corral's departure in the 21-7 loss to the Bears in the Sugar Bowl.
